{
  "stem": "9156.9",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Now, in addition to that, I worked a lot with delinquents, and, you know, that's my special, and with young people.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "That's another part of people who stayed here.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And I have to say that because Minnesota, at that time, didn't have highways, and when a kid was in Red Wing, which is the delinquency institution, and had to go back home to their home up north, when it was too far-- so at night they drop them into the jail.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "We said-- I said, that's inexcusable.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "So they stayed here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "So this is-- I mean, there's lots.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now that's another thing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In 1950, the American government, you know, was the High Commissioner for Germany.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, there were French High Commissioners, English, and American, and Russian.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You remember that, right?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was divided in four parts.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the American government, I think, was incurably interested, and very rightfully so, to get away-- to do away with this horrible Nazi period, I mean, the thinking that had influenced that whole country.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they were concerned about young people, and about children, and about children's institutions.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The place was filled with those.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Child Welfare was the department under which all that went.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They also sent over Germans who were young adults, who were not Nazi, to learn, here, more.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I had a lot of Germans, a lot of Dutch, mostly, here, many other foreign students, but from that area.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Social group work, to me, I have to say, is a philosophy, not a-- and I never taught it as-- how do you call that?",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Just a little technique.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It means the incredible thing to me that you can help the individual to be him or herself, while you are still taking responsibility for others.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
